  <span id="freeText5814191846582357915" style="display:none">Delaney's sword and sandal collection builds a compelling world laden with commentary on gender, sexuality, and civilization itself. As the characters weave together across stories, we see the vicissitudes of a strange and terrible land from the perspective of outsiders, insiders, and the ignored. I can't wait to read the next entry in the series.</span>
