<li class='cover' id='bookCover_53317480'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/53317480-light-chaser"><img alt="Light Chaser" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1610386495l/53317480._SX98_.jpg" />
